trade_shows.title: PitchItTOCityHall
trade_shows.content:
"PitchItTO is an event you donâ€™t want to miss!"
PitchItTOCityHall is an exclusive closed pitch event, that includes up to five angel groups and/or Business Leaders. A showcase of 20 start-ups, Light fare and beverages, Breakout Sessions, Round Table, and Network with an audience that is comprised of entrepreneurs, angel investors, partners, and business leaders.

trade_shows.title: Longs Park Art Festival
trade_shows.content: Longs Park Art Festival is recognized as one of the best outdoor fine arts festivals on the East Coast. Volunteers and artists turn this beautiful city park into a prestigious outdoor art gallery showcasing unique, handmade fine art and crafts. Guests from the mid-Atlantic region come here to purchase works by their favorite artists and to discover their passion for artists who are new or unfamiliar to them.

trade_shows.title: SalonsCE Paris
trade_shows.content:
"With SalonsCE simplify your life"
SalonsCE Paris to offer meetings and exchanges, between elected officials of CE, CSE, representatives of staff and suppliers. Find a wide range of products and services offered by exhibitors from all over France, special offers, novelty and preferential rates. From automatic distribution, to software and CE / CSE training, through cultural outings, ticketing and travel, to gift cards or gourmet packages.. find on your show a multitude of sectors of activity.

trade_shows.title: SIAL Canada
trade_shows.content:
"Equipment technology and service exhibition for the food distribution, hotel restaurant and food service industries in Canada."
SIAL Canada aims to promote the industry's products and expertise. In addition, a colorful new event was held for the first time, on the second evening of the show: the shows VIP Evening in collaboration with renowned chef Chuck Hughes. Industry professionals gathered in a relaxed setting with a beer and cheese theme.

trade_shows.title: Global Forum for Innovations in Agriculture
trade_shows.content:
"The world's largest marketplace for sustainable agriculture"
GFIA is the region's largest exhibition and conference dealing with innovations in sustainable agriculture across all types of food production. So whether one wants to improve productivity, increase profits, save natural resources, or overcome the challenges of climate change, there are hundreds of solution providers exhibiting with working products to help your business remain competitive and sustainable for the long-term. It puts emphasis on livestock and indoor farming, hydroponics, and aquaculture as well.

Highlights
GFIA is the largest showcase of sustainable agricultural innovations in the world.
GFIA attracts decision-makers from 100+ countries right across the food value chain.
Be a part of this major expo with adjoining conferences like Cold Chain Expo, Apiarab Expo and more.

trade_shows.title: Gallery SHOES
trade_shows.content:
"The Leather and Leather Products & Accessories Industry Trade Fair"
Gallery SHOES is the international fashion trade show for footwear and accessories. This event shows products like fashion shoes, indoor shoes, casual shoes, sport shoes, leather shoes, canvas shoes, sandals, slippers, work shoes, snow boots, hiking shoes, rubber shoes etc. in the Leather & Leather Products, Lifestyle & Fashion industries.

trade_shows.title: Autumn Gift & Homeware Fair
trade_shows.content: Spring Gift & Homeware Fair is a trade-only show where retailers can view and order the latest product lines in one place, at one time. It is simply the best value for your marketing dollar and by exhibiting at two or more Gift Fairs in the calendar year you'll also enjoy special exhibition rates while growing your profile and your profits.

trade_shows.title: Taste of Amsterdam
trade_shows.content:
"A culinary heaven in the city centre of Amsterdam. This festival exceeds all expectations."
Taste of Amsterdam is showing the companies news of Netherlands and internationals related to sectors Restaurants, Natural foods, Food. This event will be beneficial for the food lover of the contemporary times. They will get an opportunity to have a face to face interaction and communication with the producers and suppliers of various kinds of food items and beverages. The face to face interaction and communication between these food lovers, producers and suppliers will give rise to new and innovative ideas.

Highlights
Chef's Table, Chef's Theater, Kookschool and several high-end restaurants and chefs from Amsterdam.

trade_shows.title: Job Fair & Training Expo
trade_shows.content:
"Looking to Hire or Recruit? Loo kinking for a Job or Career?"
The Hire Canada Job Fair & Training Expo is Canada€™s most successful & comprehensive multi sector recruitment event. We host recruitment events which introduce applicants to Recruiters, Admissions staff and Career Advisors face to face. Our events provide a great opportunity for organizations that are looking to hire, recruit or promote their brand.

Highlights
Jobs, careers, employment
Recruit, promote, hire
Continuing education, upgrade skills

trade_shows.title: Journees dentaires internationales du Quebec
trade_shows.content:
"Major and essential event for the dental profession in Canada."
Quebec International Dental Days is going to deal with all the possible services and important notifications that are highly associated with dentist industry. It is the perfect place that is going to deal with the new technologies and modalities of treatment that are associated with the field of dentistry. It is going to be a vital event which is going to invite various important visitors from different parts of the world and they are all from the professional grounds and also the normal candidates who are interested in this field.

trade_shows.title: International Exhibition for Home Interiors and Consumer Electronics HomeStyle & Electronics
trade_shows.content:
HomeStyle & Electronics makes it possible for its exhibitors to showcase their projects and products, for designers it is finding new customers and meaningful contacts, and for the visitors it is an opportunity to get the ideas of their home improvements.

Highlights
The only event of its kind to demonstrate the latest technologies of home appliances in Uzbekistan
Accompanied by the international exhibition of woodworking and furniture - MebelExpo Uzbekistan

trade_shows.title: Annual Young Child Expo & Conference
trade_shows.content:
"To help in Growth of young Children"
The Annual Young Child Expo & Conference promises to be another highly rated inspiring professional development opportunity. It provides the opportunity to learn effective interventions for young children from a wide range of experts.

trade_shows.title: Job Fair

trade_shows.title: Newcastle Upon Tyne Jobs Fair
trade_shows.content:
"Face to face recruitment"
Newcastle Upon Tyne Jobs Fair event attracts a mixture of different employers from various industries all recruiting for local jobs. The Newcastle Careers Fair is a great way to speak with potential employers face-to-face. You can register with employers for jobs, collect info on employers, ask them questions, apply for jobs, or even have a mini-interview on the day.

Mini interviews on the day
Make a great first impression in-person

"Port Harcourt international Education Fair 2019"
The Port-Harcourt Education Fair brings exciting opportunities for students wishing to study abroad by bringing institutions from all around the world to one place; giving students wishing to study abroad more opportunities and options, thereby attracting a high number of students. Lekkside has a history of nearly 10 years excellence in education.

trade_shows.title: Travel Expos
trade_shows.content: Travel Expo will bring in thousands of Village residents, allowing them the opportunity to meet face to face with in-state, national, and international travel destinations, hotels, tour operators, cruise lines and attractions for new vacation ideas in the coming years.

trade_shows.title: Legal Affairs Conference
trade_shows.content:
Legal Affairs Conference will provide participants with the opportunity to exchange views and share ideas with leading industry executives and experts, counsel and European institution officials around the latest developments in intellectual property and legal affairs concerning generic, biosimilar and value-added medicines within Europe and worldwide. Take up the opportunity to attend this event and join in shaping discussions at the interactive roundtables on topics that will include competition policies, Brexit, second medical use patents, artificial intelligence and IP, the 505(b)(2) system in the US, and more.

Highlights
Discussion around the latest developments on Supplementary Protection Certificate (SPC) Regulation
Focus on the challenges and opportunities on biosimilars in Europe and the US
Reflection on patent quality & the European patent system
Review of the existing patent linkages in the EU Member States
High level General Counsel discussion

trade_shows.title: Africa ICS Cybersecurity Conference and Expo
trade_shows.content:
"Securing ICS, SCADA in digital transformation and innovation era"
Africa ICS Cybersecurity Conference and Expo is the only platform that will proudly present the top-level B2B and B2C networking opportunities. This platform will GUARANTEES our sponsors and exhibitors a one to one meeting with top-level buyers within the African Market and beyond. It’s the only platform you will find top-level government officials, Private sector CEOs, Researchers and Innovators. Meaning the event is a crucial opportunity for buyers, vendors, and experts to attend.

Highlights
High-Level Plenary Sessions
Track Sessions
Africa ICS/SCADA Business meeting
Side workshops
Africa Women in Cybersecurity Forum

trade_shows.title: Baby Expo
trade_shows.content:
"Baby Expo is a foothold for your business"
